{"type": "article", "id": 23404, "title": "如今全世界的同人作者，都在为这一对疯狂", "description": "我已经忘了胡歌和霍建华了，嗯。", "date": "2016-03-08T08:00:02Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 22876, "name": "疯狂动物城"}, {"id": 16264, "name": "同人"}], "category": 3, "author": 130547, "comment_count": 26, "praise_count": 495, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606071155313MC1szXYWn2L8l9P.gif", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">你看《疯狂动物城》了吗？——这两天大家见面的问候语已经变成了这句。随着迪士尼的这部动画片在全球上映，小动物们已经获得了各国粉丝的喜爱。</p>\n<p class=\"\">而除了做到了“故事技巧满分”、“动画代表全球最高水平”、“完美隐喻人类社会”等等，这部动画片还在 2016 年刚开始就带来了一对最萌 CP——兔警官朱迪 VS 混混狐尼克。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607115512KiZxLow6ulDVTrUS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.41851852\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">“胡萝卜小姐”太萌太元气，而“吊梢眼先生”太酷太帅又太会撩妹——不管电影里演没演，反正同人作者们纷纷少女/男心爆棚了。</p>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: left;\">这两天，微博、Tumblr、Twitter 都已经被这一对的同人图攻陷。美国艺术交流社区 Deviantart 上设置了 Nick X Judy 专区。\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n在粉丝们的创作里，所有你想要的——都有了！</p>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><b>好了，不多说了，多图预警。</b></p>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">赶快先来几张甜的！</span><br></p>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: left;\">冰淇淋梗，看的要融化了。来自 Tumblr 的网友@gugugudraw 。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071155130SE9mC5sdLzxhPB7.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74907407\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">不给你吃嘿嘿嘿。</div></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607115514MarNu0AJsbSjyiE5.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.826\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">吃到了哈哈哈。<a href=\"http://gugugudraw.tumblr.com/post/140553892674/zootopia%E5%A5%BD%E5%A5%BD%E7%9C%8B-%E7%8B%90%E7%8B%B8%E5%85%94%E5%AD%90%E5%A4%AA%E7%94%9C%E4%BA%86\">@gugugudraw</a>\n</div></figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607115515UzxqcMEtAoSXibhd.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.414\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Hello Mr.Fox<a href=\"http://www.pixiv.net/member.php?id=3727139\">  @尤石馬</a>\n</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">结婚！结婚！结婚！<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607115515adr0ohF8yjYQA9Gp.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"2.06673843\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<span style=\"text-align: justify;\"></span><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607115516dIRHycsVxKEjiGNL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.308\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">姑娘，你耳朵能耷拉点吗？</span></p>\n<p class=\"\"><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">不行，我心情正好。</span></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607115516AHGTSbhU6Mfsy108.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.22\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://danji-doodle.tumblr.com/post/140570080449/i-went-to-see-zootopia-3-3-3-perfect-family\">@ssaldanji</a></div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">此处无声胜有声。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"placeholder\"></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607115516kQmlJtaYOGcwLjuD.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">@<a href=\"http://40.media.tumblr.com/eab8774e27ec6739fc7bcc61c0325367/tumblr_o31skycs6P1u7e1hfo1_1280.jpg\">thebronyphilospher</a>\n</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">Deviantart 上的韩国网友 @Ganym0 画了朱迪反攻的场景。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607115517CF8xs7qBtLyuYMEQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0814901\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607115517uSztHjR6E3vC4ZlN.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.83452503\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607115518e1wH7LMPT0kKR56a.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.09287926\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607115518HUC4FBbfvSMwzGm6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.02898551\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607115519T02xZqlXrdmf8HRh.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70512821\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">Twitter 网友<a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23ByronHoward\"> @ByronHoward </a>的画风很复古。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607115519eWyEPQINYHF7DtBM.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55706522\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">你被捕了！</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607115520Zh2mbtzqR3PEweMH.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.005\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">羊姐</div></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071155204PuG2o36SXykY9CB.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55298913\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">小人国。</div></figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607115521wsBagN3AR65S91kU.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.23666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">《神秘博士》版</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">吃 Pocky 绝对是百试不爽的梗啊。<br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071155211gmc5A6LsiZa2OvX.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"3.40425532\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://spikeout.tumblr.com/post/140565239012/artwork-by-siam%E8%B2%9D\">@siam貝</a></div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: left;\">如果要同居，第一个问题是床太小……<a href=\"http://theartmanor.tumblr.com/post/140593213768/judy-bringing-nick-over-to-her-apartment-for-the\">@theartmanor </a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607115522IRZ7nwaUM0ydDpNq.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.916\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">尼克：那啥……你说床很小不是开玩笑的。朱迪：是啊。我们得挤一挤。</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607115522JOExnlq9UTGZBXiz.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.81296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">朱迪：快点。我们明天还要早起工作。</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071155231qUifr97Ft8zsPXc.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.91666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">尼克：呵呵，晚安，拥抱大师！ 朱迪：闭嘴！晚安。</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">这张好萌！</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607115523UdWwag2pOL01Heyb.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.41512605\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://images6.fanpop.com/image/photos/38500000/Judy-and-Nick-disneys-zootopia-38591829-595-842.jpg\">fanpop.com</a></div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">这张更萌！</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607115524IUXrNHZonBzs8VKT.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.31018519\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://orange2930.tumblr.com/post/140585866338/%E9%80%99%E5%80%8B%E6%A7%8B%E5%9C%96%E5%A4%AA%E5%8F%AF%E6%84%9B%E6%88%91%E5%B0%B1%E7%95%AB%E3%84%8C%E6%B7%9A%E6%B5%81%E6%BB%BF%E9%9D%A2\">@orange2930</a></p></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">“大家好，这是我的女朋友。”</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607115524XgecP9VQB3mhTCar.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">“我女朋友靠着我肩膀睡着了。好萌~”<a href=\"http://xnxf003.tumblr.com/post/140567272208/%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%A4%E5%BC%A0%E7%9A%84%E5%B0%B1%E5%BE%80%E6%B1%A4%E4%B8%8A%E6%94%BE%E5%90%A7%E7%AD%89%E5%87%91%E4%B9%9D%E4%BA%86%E5%86%8D%E5%8F%91%E5%BE%AE%E5%8D%9A%E5%87%91%E6%95%B0%E5%96%82%D0%B7%E3%82%9D\">@侠女小方</a>\n</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">“真人”版。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607115525poYz0k7T2WvxmgIa.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/pentadpower/status/702764673582522369\">@pentadpower</a></div></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607115525prRELGcKfk9M1Ze0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607115526AMYWl7mH0Pbikg5F.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://mohtz.tumblr.com/post/140553453176/z\">@stephanie</a></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071155263WqfTGm0l1oFKQUO.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50278293\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607115526z5GRwXnF2CSjbgD3.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50300601\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://astridyyx.tumblr.com/post/140561227589/bunny-estrus-w\">@astridyyx</a></div></figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607115527x0GrfLdcuZY3K7aP.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.48\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://spoonkid.tumblr.com/post/140606761011/judynike\">@spoonkid</a></p></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<span style=\"text-align: justify;\"></span><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607115528qJxE1Qpnw9tmAe3S.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.834\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.google.com.sg/url?sa=i&amp;rct=j&amp;q=&amp;esrc=s&amp;source=images&amp;cd=&amp;ved=0ahUKEwiVzqDmk67LAhWBNKYKHcaxBBoQjxwIAw&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tumblr.com%2Ftagged%2Fnick-on-the-draw&amp;psig=AFQjCNFx3ZEFsi9wwzgteusxcAXPf-TKKQ&amp;ust=1457425652339785\" class=\"\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">@ diaemyung</a></div></figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">“真动物”版。</span></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<span style=\"text-align: justify;\"></span><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607115528xOZihf7R8nt9Dvs2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.83\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://36.media.tumblr.com/0d31066c24c8c25650f532619043157c/tumblr_inline_nq680q8QZK1t0ops6_540.jpg\">tumblr</a></div></figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">娃都生了。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607115529oqLMvpTCVrcNzhI4.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.41363636\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://miyakuli.tumblr.com/post/140595060965/permission-to-post-it-was-granted-by-the-artist\" class=\"\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">@miyakuli</a></div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">重口的还能没有吗？</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607115529y8MjcmVXHTbz9u7l.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.16009281\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://movie.douban.com/photos/photo/2323698122/\">图片来自豆瓣</a></div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">纯纯的也很满足：如果我可以参与你的童年……<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607115530kJEhdUgGqBtx1CKj.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://tenyai.tumblr.com/post/140608139447/i-just-had-to-paint-this-because-i-love-this-movie\">@tenyai</a></div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">当然了，其它角色也很赞。最后来插播两张“羊姐”和“骚气虎”。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607115530l57FEHYCSnvyDdci.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.16666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://e621.net/post/show/843705/disney-feline-male-mammal-solo-stripper_tiger_-zoo\">@ seiryuuden</a></div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607115530EniNWVgK0d4Txt37.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.4\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/CXAqT2xWAAAvKiC.jpg\">twimg.com</a></div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">想看小说版？你还可以去<a href=\"https://www.fanfiction.net/s/11824744/1/The-Funnies-or-Boxes-Diaries\"> Fanfiction </a>和<a href=\"http://s.weibo.com/weibo/%25E7%2596%25AF%25E7%258B%2582%25E5%258A%25A8%25E7%2589%25A9%25E5%259F%258E%2520%25E5%2590%258C%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2596%2587&amp;Refer=STopic_box\">微博</a>上看同人文。什么尺度的都有了。</p>\n<p class=\"\">我想，作者@tenyai 的话能够总结大家的疯狂——“我太爱这部电影了！”<br></p>\n<p class=\"\">图片来源：pinterest,tumblr,deviantart，twitter，giphy，豆瓣电影<br></p>\n\n\n"}